{"title":"LAC - Formal Languages and Automata Theory 形式语言与自动机理论","uid":"49266c0927eaad653ea21227e55d59fb","slug":"LAC-形式语言与自动机","date":"2024-05-25T10:53:20.000Z","updated":"2024-05-25T11:09:13.929Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/LAC-形式语言与自动机.json","keywords":null,"cover":"\\img\\cover\\LAC.png","content":"<h1>背景</h1>\n<p>课程原名为Languages and Computation(语言与计算)，但是这很明显是一个比较笼统的名字。本课程的主要内容还是将有关形式语言与自动机理论的知识。</p>\n<p>关于自动机，早在学习算法竞赛的时候有学过AC自动机(Aho-Corasick automaton, 是字典树 + KMP算法 + 自动机的结合)的知识，但是并没有建立有关自动机的系统性概念。</p>\n<p>此外，在学习做游戏AI的时候，有接触过关于状态设计模式的概念，游戏AI是一个巨大的状态自动机，因此我也利用这个方法在我CPP课程的游戏里设计了敌人的AI，具体可以参考这个笔记: <a href=\"\">简单游戏引擎开发笔记</a>。</p>\n<h1>介绍</h1>\n<h2 id=\"本笔记主要分为下面几个部分-并不是按照课程顺序排序，而是相似课程归纳-：\">本笔记主要分为下面几个部分(并不是按照课程顺序排序，而是相似课程归纳)：</h2>\n","feature":false,"text":"有关形式语言与自动机理论的课程笔记。...","permalink":"/post/LAC-形式语言与自动机","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":323,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"笔记","slug":"笔记","count":3,"path":"api/categories/笔记.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Notes","slug":"Notes","count":3,"path":"api/tags/Notes.json"},{"name":"Automata Theory","slug":"Automata-Theory","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Automata-Theory.json"},{"name":"Formal Languages","slug":"Formal-Languages","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Formal-Languages.json"},{"name":"Theory","slug":"Theory","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Theory.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\"><span class=\"toc-text\">背景</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\"><span class=\"toc-text\">介绍</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%9C%AC%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%8B%E9%9D%A2%E5%87%A0%E4%B8%AA%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86-%E5%B9%B6%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E6%8C%89%E7%85%A7%E8%AF%BE%E7%A8%8B%E9%A1%BA%E5%BA%8F%E6%8E%92%E5%BA%8F%EF%BC%8C%E8%80%8C%E6%98%AF%E7%9B%B8%E4%BC%BC%E8%AF%BE%E7%A8%8B%E5%BD%92%E7%BA%B3-%EF%BC%9A\"><span class=\"toc-text\">本笔记主要分为下面